t: Me Jane | The Gyaru Wiki | Fandom
s: Me Jane (ミージェーン) is a Japanese clothing brand established in 1990[1]. It was founded by SAJA CO,.LTD and holds headquarters in Tokyo. It is known for its sleeveless faux fur jackets and clothing produced in the 2000's. It is very popular with Tsuyome Gyaru, Onee-Gyaru and Ane Gyaru.
